 One possible military use of orion is to make a space<br>
faring space plane, and missile carrier. A science fiction example of this idea up to a point  could be the colonial <br>
battlestars or the ceylon  base stars potrayed<br>
in the battle star galactica science fiction movies.<br>
<br>
 Some one  could for example make a 300,000 ,000 pound<br>
pound orion nuclear pulse rocket with a 3/1 mass ratio<br>
that is powerd by the detonation of one to  10 megaton fusion  pulse units. There could be 200,000,000 pounds<br>
 worth of pulse units stored in perhaps a 40,000,000 pound <br>
magizine, and there might be a 10,000,000 pound impulse<br>
abscorber pusher plate system. This makes availible a <br>
payload weight of 50,000,000 pounds which is 25,000 tons<br>
<br>
 You could make a modern H-bomb with a maximium weight<br>
of 1000 kilograms, and perhaps a 5 or 10 megaton yield.<br>
You could place them on solid fueled missiles and carry them around the solar system on orion nuclear pulse drive battlestars .<br>
<br>
  If we assume a weight of 10,000 pounds per solid fueled<br>
 missile then for a weight of 10,000,000 pounds we could carry an arsenal of 1000 of these missiles around the solar system on orion. We could also carry an arsenal of perhaps 50 or 100 20 ton nuclear thermal propulsion manned space planes on an orion. <br>
<br>
100 20 ton space planes would weigh 2000 tons, which is<br>
4,000,000 pounds. The space planes could have an ion drive for interplanetary space use, and a nuclear thermal drive for flying down to planets to attack them.They would have a space shuttle style heat shield, and they could be armed with chemical powered laser guns, missiles, and multiple  atomic, or thermonuclear weapons (bombs, and missiles ).<br>
<br>
I do not advocate making such space warships. I merely <br>
wish to point out the reality of this possibility.I will also<br>
say that if we Americans do not do this first, that we better hope it will not be the  future communist  super power of China, or a future radical Islamic empire or islamic  super power<br>
that has not been created yet that will do this first in the future.    <br>
<br>
 Perhaps the communist will someday  say we are going to do all these things and then we shall wipe out the western capitalist/democratic  alliance  , and then we shall  proceed to conquer and rule  the solar system and the earth with a rod of iron . <br>
<br>
 Or perhaps the muslims will one day build orion etc,<br>
and  then they will say to them infidels (all non Muslims)<br>
 that we must do all these things, and then proceed  to conquer, and rule the earth, and all the solar system in the name of allah, and then they will carry it out<br>
in practice against us americans europeans , and others. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#6F6F6F>- </font><a href=http://pub97.ezboard.com/bnuclearspace>NuclearSpace Message Board</a><font color=#6F6F6F> - </font><a href=http://pub97.ezboard.com/fnuclearspacefrm3>Asteroid Watch & General Astronomy</a> <font color=#6F6F6F> - </font><a href="http://www.nuclearspace.com">NuclearSpace Home Page</a><font color=#6F6F6F> - </font><br><br><table border=0 align=center><tr><td align=center><a href="http://login.ezboard.com/BBSSystem.showUserPaymentScreen" target="_blank">Upgrade your account to ezSupporter...</a></td><td><img src="http://www.ezboard.com/image/spacer.gif" width=15 height=1 border=0></td><td align=center><a href="http://login.ezboard.com/BBSSystem.showUserPaymentScreen" target="_blank">...and never see another ad or pop-up again</a></td></tr></table><CENTER><!-- START BOTTOM AD SCRIPT -->
